item.title: Where Have I Been? (2024 Edition)
item.description: I have not been posting a lot on this blog for quite a while now. This is not because I have stopped being interested in writing. Quite the opposite actually. I have been working with other companies like BetterStack and CodeCrafter’s OSS History to create articles for them. I have also been working on several big projects like my Technical Interview Study Guide and Omashu. I have several articles in mind that I would like to post on this blog so stay tuned!
